<div class="curved" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;padding:20px;float:right;width:530px;">
Welcome to <b>S.H. Kelkar's</b><div style="font-size:18pt;padding:0 0 10px 0"><b>F</b>ormulation <b>A</b>dministration <b>S</b>ystem</div>
